rows.label: tlk00340109_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey! The rookie you picked
out is doing a great job.

rows.label: tlk00340109_msg0002
rows.name:
That Fisena is not only good at her
job, she's great at livening things
up. A real star at celebrations.

rows.label: tlk00340109_msg0003
rows.name:
Powapowa's work is so-so, but she
works hard to soothe the hearts of
the mercenaries returning from battle.

rows.label: tlk00340109_msg0004
rows.name:
Zengrid is great with managing
money. He's working hard to
eliminate wasteful spending.

rows.label: tlk00340109_msg0005
rows.name:
Complete some more missions,
and we'll trust you with
another important job.

rows.label: tlk00340109_msg0006
rows.name:
Make sure you come back to the
village every now and then!
